00:00:12.972 --> 00:00:18.441
Hi! Welcome to your favorite show Aha Emi Ruchi

00:00:37.163 --> 00:00:40.241
What are you going to cook for us today?
Chilli Mutton

00:00:58.816 --> 00:01:01.171
Ingredients required for Chilli Mutton

00:01:01.171 --> 00:01:12.605
Mutton, Ginger Garlic Paste, Coriander Leaves,
 Green Chillies, Curry Leaves, Cashew Nuts,
 Turmeric Powder, Garlic, Garam Masala &amp; Oil

00:01:37.254 --> 00:01:53.228
First grind some ginger, garlic and cumin seeds into a paste
 and add it to the boiled mutton pieces &amp; keep it aside

00:01:58.775 --> 00:02:04.769
Heat some oil in a pan 

00:02:10.964 --> 00:02:16.893
Add some chopped garlic pieces and curry leaves into the pan

00:02:23.785 --> 00:02:28.531
Add some chopped green chillies into the pan

00:02:37.202 --> 00:02:43.632
Add some cashew nuts into the pan 
&amp; fry them for a while

00:03:00.041 --> 00:03:05.781
Add some turmeric powder into the pan &amp; mix well

00:03:08.605 --> 00:03:22.037
Now add the boiled mutton mix into the pan 

00:03:29.260 --> 00:03:33.025
Add some turmeric powder into the pan and mix well

00:03:39.007 --> 00:03:45.609
Add some garam masala into the pan &amp; mix well

00:03:51.145 --> 00:03:58.370
Now close the pan with a lid &amp; cook it for five minutes

00:04:11.341 --> 00:04:16.498
Add some coriander leaves into the pan &amp; mix well

00:04:18.746 --> 00:04:23.519
Now take the Chilli Mutton into a serving bowl

